description: Today I'm showing you how to make my vegan beet burgers! This veggie burger recipe is packed full of grated beetroot, lentils, oats, and more for a hearty, deeply flavourful veggie burger patty. These beet veggie burgers are also a fun red colour! I hope you enjoy my beet burger recipe :)
name: Vegan Beet Burgers - Veggie Burger Recipe
